  "title": "Intensely Sweet Saudi Arabian Date Tart",
  "description": "A sweet and bouncy dessert featuring creme patissiere and dates, perfect for a special night, this dish is ayurvedic sattvic friendly and made with mantecare emulsify method.",
  "cuisine": "Saudi Arabian",
