  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a bowl, whisk together flour, sugar, and cardamom powder.",
    "Add melted butter and mix until a crumbly mixture forms.",
    "Press the mixture into a tart pan with a removable bottom.",
    "Arrange the dates on top of the crust.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together creme patissiere, eggs, and rose water.",
    "Pour the creme patissiere mixture over the dates.",
    "Bake the tart for 40 minutes or until the crust is golden brown.",
    "Allow the tart to cool before serving.",
    "Dust with powdered sugar before serving."
